              
-------------------------Trivia Game---------------------------

Trivia game contains programing questions

for storage we use sql DB sqlite3
to store our game questions ,answers and leaderboard 

for our gui we are using PyQt4

we use python3 version for this game 

to start the game you have the makefile 

first open your command line in the game folder and run

the command make

after that use the command

make install and then you are setup to start the game from any where

just opne the command line and write start.py

and you can start playing.


to remove the game just go to  /usr/local/bin/

and delete start.py game.py logo.py sql.py files

